#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.memory_usage.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.memory\\_usage"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:1 of
msgid "Return the memory usage of the Series."
msgstr "返回 Series 的内存使用情况。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:3 of
msgid ""
"The memory usage can optionally include the contribution of the index and"
" of elements of `object` dtype."
msgstr "内存使用情况可以可选地包括索引和 `object` 类型元素的贡献。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:6 of
msgid "Specifies whether to include the memory usage of the Series index."
msgstr "指定是否包括 Series 索引的内存使用情况。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:8 of
msgid ""
"If True, introspect the data deeply by interrogating `object` dtypes for "
"system-level memory consumption, and include it in the returned value."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则通过查询 `object` 类型来深入分析数据的系统级内存消耗，并将"
"其包含在返回值中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:13 of
msgid "Bytes of memory consumed."
msgstr "消耗的内存字节数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.ndarray.nbytes`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:19 of
msgid "Total bytes consumed by the elements of the array."
msgstr "数组元素消耗的总字节数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.memory_usage`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:22 of
msgid "Bytes consumed by a DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 消耗的字节数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:31 of
msgid ""
"Not including the index gives the size of the rest of the data, which is "
"necessarily smaller:"
msgstr "不包括索引时给出其余数据的大小，这必然更小："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.series_memory_usage:37 of
msgid "The memory footprint of `object` values is ignored by default:"
msgstr "默认情况下会忽略 `object` 值的内存占用："

